act: An Act to amend the Criminal Code (mental disorder) and to make consequential amendments to other Acts
precis:
Order fixing dates on which the provisions of this Act [Bill C-10], being chapter 22 of the Statutes of Canada, 2005, COME INTO FORCE, as follows:

(a) JUNE 30, 2005 - sections 1 to 7, 10, 11, 33, 40, 49, 58 to 60 and 63; and
(b) JANUARY 2, 2006 - all other sections, other than section 64.
